  "texts": [
    "In all the cases, the refined prompts demonstrated greater accuracy in the answer.",
    "For BPMN model representation, the difference in accuracy between the not refined prompts and refined prompts cases is significant, exhibiting a high influence of the prompts refinement level on the obtained results.",
    "RQ3: How does the choice of process representation format and related embedding model affect the performance of the BPLLM?In tackling RQ3, we delved into the impact of the process representation format and corresponding embedding model on the accuracy of the BPLLM pipeline.",
